title: Brady, Patriots pull away from Romo-less Cowboys 30-6
text:
> Texas Brady, Patriots pull away from Romo-less Cowboys 30-6 Dallas Cowboys' Dez Bryant, right, who is recovering from an injury, watches from the sideline during the first quarter of an NFL football game against the New England Patriots, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015, in Arlington, Texas. (AP Photo/Brandon Wade)
